<p><img src="{{ site.baseurl }}/assets/images/vim-stuck-insert-mode.jpg" alt="Vim Stuck in Insert Mode" /></p>

<p>As seen <a href="https://superuser.com/questions/129900/vim-stuck-in-insert-mode" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>

<p>I find out that when I copy/paste something in insert mode. I make the mistake of typing <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ctrl + s</code>.</p>

<p>To get out, use <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ctrl + q</code>.</p>

